FINAL-PLAN
------------------------------
{
  "domain": "(define (domain scheduling-domain)\n  (:requirements :strips :typing)\n  (:types agent room time meeting)\n\n  (:predicates\n    (agent ?a - agent)\n    (room ?r - room)\n    (time ?t - time)\n    (meeting ?m - meeting)\n\n    ;; availability predicates: an agent or room is free at a particular time\n    (free-agent ?a - agent ?t - time)\n    (free-room ?r - room ?t - time)\n\n    ;; meeting status\n    (unscheduled ?m - meeting)\n    (scheduled ?m - meeting ?r - room ?t - time)\n  )\n\n  ;; Schedule a meeting that requires two attendees. Preconditions ensure the\n  ;; meeting is currently unscheduled, the room is free at the chosen time, and\n  ;; both attendees are free at that time. Effects mark the meeting scheduled\n  ;; and make the room and attendees busy (remove their free facts).\n  (:action schedule-meeting-2attendees\n    :parameters (?m - meeting ?r - room ?t - time ?a1 - agent ?a2 - agent)\n    :precondition (and\n      (unscheduled ?m)\n      (free-room ?r ?t)\n      (free-agent ?a1 ?t)\n      (free-agent ?a2 ?t)\n    )\n    :effect (and\n      (not (unscheduled ?m))\n      (scheduled ?m ?r ?t)\n      (not (free-room ?r ?t))\n      (not (free-agent ?a1 ?t))\n      (not (free-agent ?a2 ?t))\n    )\n  )\n\n  ;; Schedule a meeting that requires a single attendee. Same semantics as\n  ;; above but for one attendee.\n  (:action schedule-meeting-1attendee\n    :parameters (?m - meeting ?r - room ?t - time ?a - agent)\n    :precondition (and\n      (unscheduled ?m)\n      (free-room ?r ?t)\n      (free-agent ?a ?t)\n    )\n    :effect (and\n      (not (unscheduled ?m))\n      (scheduled ?m ?r ?t)\n      (not (free-room ?r ?t))\n      (not (free-agent ?a ?t))\n    )\n  )\n)\n",
  "problem_first_instance": "(define (problem schedule-instance-1)\n  (:domain scheduling-domain)\n  (:objects\n    alice bob - agent\n    r1 - room\n    t1 t2 - time\n    m1 - meeting\n  )\n\n  ;; Observations / initial state for the first instance\n  ;; \"unscheduled\" encodes that the meeting still needs scheduling.\n  ;; free-agent and free-room facts encode only times that are available.\n  ;; Times not listed for an agent/room are treated as unavailable.\n  (:init\n    ;; type declarations (explicit facts help readability)\n    (agent alice)\n    (agent bob)\n    (room r1)\n    (time t1)\n    (time t2)\n    (meeting m1)\n\n    ;; meeting m1 has not been scheduled yet\n    (unscheduled m1)\n\n    ;; Availability according to observed facts:\n    ;; Alice is free at t1 and t2\n    (free-agent alice t1)\n    (free-agent alice t2)\n\n    ;; Bob is unavailable at t1 (no free-agent bob t1 fact)\n    ;; Bob is free at t2\n    (free-agent bob t2)\n\n    ;; Room r1 is unavailable at t1 and free at t2\n    (free-room r1 t2)\n  )\n\n  ;; Goal: schedule meeting m1 at the earliest time that satisfies constraints.\n  ;; Given the observations, the earliest feasible time is t2.\n  (:goal (and (scheduled m1 r1 t2)))\n)\n",
  "problem_second_instance": "(define (problem schedule-instance-2)\n  (:domain scheduling-domain)\n  (:objects\n    dave elena - agent\n    rA rB - room\n    t1 t2 t3 - time\n    m2 - meeting\n  )\n\n  ;; Observations / initial state for the second instance.\n  ;; Availability is encoded only where explicitly observed free; missing\n  ;; free facts denote unavailable slots and must not be treated as free.\n  (:init\n    ;; type facts\n    (agent dave)\n    (agent elena)\n    (room rA)\n    (room rB)\n    (time t1)\n    (time t2)\n    (time t3)\n    (meeting m2)\n\n    ;; meeting m2 still needs scheduling\n    (unscheduled m2)\n\n    ;; Observed availability:\n    ;; Dave is unavailable at t1 (no fact); free at t2 and t3\n    (free-agent dave t2)\n    (free-agent dave t3)\n\n    ;; Elena is unavailable at t2 (no fact); free at t1 and t3\n    (free-agent elena t1)\n    (free-agent elena t3)\n\n    ;; Room availability observed:\n    ;; rA is free only at t3 (rA unavailable at t1 and t2)\n    (free-room rA t3)\n    ;; rB is free at t1, t2, and t3\n    (free-room rB t1)\n    (free-room rB t2)\n    (free-room rB t3)\n  )\n\n  ;; Goal: schedule meeting m2 with both attendees. The earliest time when\n  ;; both Dave and Elena are free is t3; a room available at t3 is required.\n  ;; rA and rB are both available at t3; choose rB (both are acceptable, but\n  ;; the goal constrains a particular chosen room to reflect the observed\n  ;; preference/constraint decision). We require scheduling at t3.\n  (:goal (and (scheduled m2 rB t3)))\n)\n"
}

<domain>
(define (domain scenario_domain)
  (:requirements :typing :negative-preconditions :strips)
  (:types obj)

  (:predicates
    (hand ?o - obj)
    (cats ?o - obj)
    (texture ?o - obj)
    (vase ?o1 - obj ?o2 - obj)
    (next ?o1 - obj ?o2 - obj)
    (sneeze ?o - obj)
    (spring ?o - obj)
    (collect ?o1 - obj ?o2 - obj)
    (stupendous ?o - obj)
  )

  ;; Paltry: params (hand_obj, cats_obj, texture_obj)
  ;; pre: hand ?h, cats ?c, texture ?t, vase ?h ?c, next ?c ?t
  ;; eff: add next ?h ?t, del vase ?h ?c
  (:action paltry
    :parameters (?h - obj ?c - obj ?t - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (hand ?h)
      (cats ?c)
      (texture ?t)
      (vase ?h ?c)
      (next ?c ?t)
    )
    :effect (and
      (next ?h ?t)
      (not (vase ?h ?c))
    )
  )

  ;; Sip: params (hand_obj, cats_obj, texture_obj)
  ;; pre: hand ?h, cats ?c, texture ?t, next ?h ?t, next ?c ?t
  ;; eff: add vase ?h ?c, del next ?h ?t
  (:action sip
    :parameters (?h - obj ?c - obj ?t - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (hand ?h)
      (cats ?c)
      (texture ?t)
      (next ?h ?t)
      (next ?c ?t)
    )
    :effect (and
      (vase ?h ?c)
      (not (next ?h ?t))
    )
  )

  ;; Clip: params (hand_obj, sneeze_obj, texture_obj)
  ;; pre: hand ?h, sneeze ?s, texture ?t, next ?s ?t, next ?h ?t
  ;; eff: add vase ?h ?s, del next ?h ?t
  (:action clip
    :parameters (?h - obj ?s - obj ?t - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (hand ?h)
      (sneeze ?s)
      (texture ?t)
      (next ?s ?t)
      (next ?h ?t)
    )
    :effect (and
      (vase ?h ?s)
      (not (next ?h ?t))
    )
  )

  ;; Wretched: params (sneeze_subject, texture1, texture2, stupendous_obj)
  ;; pre: sneeze ?s0, texture ?t1, texture ?t2, stupendous ?stp, next ?s0 ?t1, collect ?t1 ?stp, collect ?t2 ?stp
  ;; eff: add next ?s0 ?t2, del next ?s0 ?t1
  (:action wretched
    :parameters (?s0 - obj ?t1 - obj ?t2 - obj ?stp - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (sneeze ?s0)
      (texture ?t1)
      (texture ?t2)
      (stupendous ?stp)
      (next ?s0 ?t1)
      (collect ?t1 ?stp)
      (collect ?t2 ?stp)
    )
    :effect (and
      (next ?s0 ?t2)
      (not (next ?s0 ?t1))
    )
  )

  ;; Memory: params (cats_obj, spring1, spring2)
  ;; pre: cats ?c, spring ?s1, spring ?s2, next ?c ?s1
  ;; eff: add next ?c ?s2, del next ?c ?s1
  (:action memory
    :parameters (?c - obj ?s1 - obj ?s2 - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (cats ?c)
      (spring ?s1)
      (spring ?s2)
      (next ?c ?s1)
    )
    :effect (and
      (next ?c ?s2)
      (not (next ?c ?s1))
    )
  )

  ;; Tightfisted: params (hand_obj, sneeze_obj, texture_obj)
  ;; pre: hand ?h, sneeze ?s, texture ?t, next ?s ?t, vase ?h ?s
  ;; eff: add next ?h ?t, del vase ?h ?s
  (:action tightfisted
    :parameters (?h - obj ?s - obj ?t - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (hand ?h)
      (sneeze ?s)
      (texture ?t)
      (next ?s ?t)
      (vase ?h ?s)
    )
    :effect (and
      (next ?h ?t)
      (not (vase ?h ?s))
    )
  )
)

(define (domain scenario_domain)
  (:requirements :typing :negative-preconditions :strips)
  (:types obj)

  (:predicates
    (hand ?o - obj)
    (cats ?o - obj)
    (texture ?o - obj)
    (vase ?o1 - obj ?o2 - obj)
    (next ?o1 - obj ?o2 - obj)
    (sneeze ?o - obj)
    (spring ?o - obj)
    (collect ?o1 - obj ?o2 - obj)
    (stupendous ?o - obj)
  )

  ;; Paltry: params (hand_obj, cats_obj, texture_obj)
  ;; pre: hand ?h, cats ?c, texture ?t, vase ?h ?c, next ?c ?t
  ;; eff: add next ?h ?t, del vase ?h ?c
  (:action paltry
    :parameters (?h - obj ?c - obj ?t - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (hand ?h)
      (cats ?c)
      (texture ?t)
      (vase ?h ?c)
      (next ?c ?t)
    )
    :effect (and
      (next ?h ?t)
      (not (vase ?h ?c))
    )
  )

  ;; Sip: params (hand_obj, cats_obj, texture_obj)
  ;; pre: hand ?h, cats ?c, texture ?t, next ?h ?t, next ?c ?t
  ;; eff: add vase ?h ?c, del next ?h ?t
  (:action sip
    :parameters (?h - obj ?c - obj ?t - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (hand ?h)
      (cats ?c)
      (texture ?t)
      (next ?h ?t)
      (next ?c ?t)
    )
    :effect (and
      (vase ?h ?c)
      (not (next ?h ?t))
    )
  )

  ;; Clip: params (hand_obj, sneeze_obj, texture_obj)
  ;; pre: hand ?h, sneeze ?s, texture ?t, next ?s ?t, next ?h ?t
  ;; eff: add vase ?h ?s, del next ?h ?t
  (:action clip
    :parameters (?h - obj ?s - obj ?t - obj)
    :precondition (and
      (hand ?h)
      (sneeze ?s)
      (texture ?t)
      (next ?s ?t)
      (next ?h ?t)
    )
    :effect (and
      (vase ?h ?s)
      (not (next ?h ?t))
    )
  )

  ;; Wretched: params (sneeze_subject, texture1, texture2, stupendous_obj)
  ;; pre: sneeze ?s0, texture ?t1, texture ?t2, stupendous ?stp, next ?s0 ?t1, collect ?t1 ?stp, collect ?t2 ?stp
